Video Stream Server Benchmark: postfix + smtp-source

1. Install the postfix in the server:
	sudo apt-get install postfix
	During the installation, select "Internet Site"

2. Install the postfix in the client:
	sudo apt-get install postfix

3. Test mail server:
	sendmail root@nebula-client.novalocal
	write mail
	ctrl + d to quit
	receive mail in /var/mail/root in nebula-client.novalocal

4. Generate and mail from client to server:
	smtp-source -s 20 -l 5120000 -m 1000 -c -f root@nebula-client.novalocal -t root@nebula-server.novalocal nebula-server.novalocal:25

Note: if using ip address as the mail address, add the following in /etc/postfix/main.cf:
	resolve_numeric_domain = yes
Then reload postfix:
	/etc/init.d/postfix reload

